      </div>
    
          <div class="card-inset-details__teaser-text">
        
            It&#039;s hard for a lot of people to imagine how they&#039;ll feel in the future, but making positive predictions could be good for their long-term psychological well-being. 
      
      </div>
    
  </div>

</article>


  
    

